title: Aoki Uru (Uru in Blue)
synopsis: In March 1992, Gainax had begun planning and production of an anime movie called Aoki Uru ("Blue Uru"), which was to be a sequel to Royal Space Force: The Wings of Honneamise set 50 years later, which, like Oritsu, would follow a group of fighter pilots.
related_anime: ['Aoki Uru: Overture', 'Ouritsu Uchuugun: Honneamise no Tsubasa']
